als - Box Score - December 26, 2015 - ESPN|publisher=ESPN}}</ref>\n|-align=center style=\"{{CollegePrimaryStyle|Louisville Cardinals|border=0|color=white}};\"\n|&nbsp;12-21-2016&nbsp; || style=\"text-align:center; {{CollegePrimaryStyle|Louisville Cardinals|border=0|color=white}};\"|[[Quentin Snider (basketball)|<span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">Quentin Snider</span>]]\n|align=left|'''Louisville''' || '''Guard|G|| 22 Points, 6 Rebounds, 5 Assists<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.espn.com/mens-college-basketball/boxscore?gameId=400910690|title=Kentucky Wildcats vs. Louisville Cardinals - Box Score - December 21, 2016 - ESPN|publisher=ESPN}}</ref>\n|-align=center style=\"{{CollegePrimaryStyle|Kentucky Wildcats|border=0|color=white}};\"\n|&nbsp;12-29-2017&nbsp; || style=\"text-align:center; {{CollegePrimaryStyle|Kentucky Wildcats|border=0|color=white}};\"|[[Shai Gilgeous-Alexander|<span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">Shai Gilgeous-Alexander</span>]]\n|align=left|'''Kentucky''' || '''Point Guard|G|| 24 Points, 5 Rebounds, 4 Assists, 3 Steals<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.aseaofblue.com/2017/12/30/16833260/shai-gilgeous-alexander-wins-mvp-award-highlights-game-louisville|title=Shai Gilgeous-Alexander wins MVP award; Highlights of his breakout game vs Louisville|work=aseaofblue.com}}</ref>\n|-align=center style=\"{{CollegePrimaryStyle|Kentucky Wildcats|border=0|color=white}};\"\n|&nbsp;12-29-2018&nbsp; || style=\"text-align:center; {{CollegePrimaryStyle|Kentucky Wildcats|border=0|color=white}};\"|[[Tyler Herro|<span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">Tyler Herro</span>]]\n|align=left|'''Kentucky''' || '''Shooting Guard|G|| 24 Points, 5 Rebounds, 2 Steals<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.kentuckysportsradio.com/basketball-2/tyler-herro-named-bluegrass-sports-commission-mvp-of-the-game/|title=Tyler Herro named Bluegrass Sports Commission MVP of the Game|work=kentuckysportsradio.com}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===Broadcast History===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Date\n! Network\n! Play-by-play\n! Analyst(s)\n